{"tid":907362,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想帶呀媽買衫 有咩造型推薦","createTime":"2018-11-18T17:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T18:04:04.000Z","uid":11834,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d84c822e3f769a59898be9b8f1bd47d60f754fb7","tid":907362,"uid":11834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"呀媽五十幾歲 一直為屋企付出好多<br />\n大部分時間都係番工同做家務，照顧屋企<br />\n所以好少打扮自己 買衫從來只係因為需要 唔係為襯衫<br />\n著既衫好多已經著左六七年以上 或者係呀妹唔著比佢<br />\n每次有重要場合佢就好苦惱 因為唔知有咩衫可以著 又唔知可以買d 咩襯衫<br />\n知道佢因為咁樣冇乜自信<br />\n所以想帶呀媽去買衫 比番d 信心佢<br />\n<br />\n所以想問咁多位巴絲 五十幾歲 身材偏瘦既女人可以去邊買衫同埋可以點襯衫？ 簡簡單單 舒服時尚就可以 <br />\n<br />\nbtw 媽咪係做收銀 所以唔慣文職太斯文look<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該哂咁多位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b961489fe198259a271229cd6e7c3edca00fa8","tid":907362,"uid":216783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo"},{"pid":"90f6c8c8dacaed195334bdbe5f5a98d2f7bd7a9a","tid":907362,"uid":56940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"COS"},{"pid":"bf5fb936be74164d85790f8062344226b756eab8","tid":907362,"uid":44823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"迷魂十字步造型<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1blt2mk/ctp-vzntr/1521599994152qoqoqrq21o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1blt2mk%2Fctp-vzntr%2F1521599994152qoqoqrq21o.jpg&h=a9afe9d9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}